{
  "info": {
    "name": "Titik Baik API",
    "description": "Koleksi lengkap endpoint backend Titik Baik – Social Donation Mapping.\n\n**Cara Pakai:**\n1. Import file environment `TitikBaik.postman_environment.json` terlebih dahulu\n2. Aktifkan environment 'Titik Baik – Development'\n3. Jalankan request **Login** (salah satu role) — token akan tersimpan otomatis\n4. Jalankan **Buat Titik Bantuan** — `point_id` tersimpan otomatis\n5. Lanjutkan pengujian endpoint lainnya\n\n**Role yang tersedia (jika sudah seed):**\n- `admin@titikbaik.id` → admin\n- `komunitas@example.com` → komunitas\n- `donatur@example.com` → donatur\n- Password semua: `password123`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "description": "Registrasi, login, dan cek token JWT.",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "Register – Donatur",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Budi Santoso\",\n  \"email\": \"budi@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"role\": \"donatur\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","auth","register"] },
            "description": "Daftarkan akun baru dengan role **donatur**.\n\n**Validasi:**\n- `name` wajib, maks 100 karakter\n- `email` harus format email valid\n- `password` minimal 8 karakter\n- `role` hanya boleh `donatur` atau `komunitas`\n\n**Response 201:** userId\n**Response 400:** validasi gagal\n**Response 409:** email sudah terdaftar"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 201\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
              "pm.test(\"Response punya userId\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property('userId');",
              "});"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Register – Komunitas",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Komunitas Peduli Yogya\",\n  \"email\": \"komunitas2@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"role\": \"komunitas\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","auth","register"] },
            "description": "Daftarkan akun baru dengan role **komunitas**."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 201\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Register – Validasi Gagal (role salah)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Test\",\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"pass\",\n  \"role\": \"superadmin\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","auth","register"] },
            "description": "Uji validasi: password terlalu pendek dan role tidak valid.\n\n**Expected:** 400 dengan `details` array berisi field yang error."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 400\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));",
              "pm.test(\"Ada field details\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property('details');",
              "});"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Login – Donatur ⚡ (auto-save token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"donatur@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] },
            "description": "Login sebagai **donatur**.\n\nToken JWT akan **otomatis tersimpan** ke environment variable `token` sehingga semua request berikutnya langsung terautentikasi.\n\n**Response 200:** token + data user\n**Response 401:** email/password salah"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "pm.test(\"Ada token\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property('token');",
              "});",
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    const body = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.environment.set('token', body.token);",
              "    console.log('✅ Token donatur tersimpan. Role:', body.user.role);",
              "}"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Login – Komunitas ⚡ (auto-save token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"komunitas@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] },
            "description": "Login sebagai **komunitas**. Token tersimpan otomatis ke `{{token}}`."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    pm.environment.set('token', pm.response.json().token);",
              "    console.log('✅ Token komunitas tersimpan');",
              "}"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Login – Admin ⚡ (auto-save token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@titikbaik.id\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] },
            "description": "Login sebagai **admin**. Token tersimpan otomatis ke `{{token}}`."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    pm.environment.set('token', pm.response.json().token);",
              "    console.log('✅ Token admin tersimpan');",
              "}"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Login – Password Salah",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"donatur@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"salah123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] },
            "description": "Uji login dengan password yang salah.\n\n**Expected:** 401"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 401\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(401));"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Cek Token (GET /me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","auth","me"] },
            "description": "Verifikasi token JWT masih valid dan lihat payload-nya (userId, role).\n\n**Expected:** 200 + data user dari token\n**Response 401:** token tidak ada / kadaluarsa"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "pm.test(\"Ada field user\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property('user');",
              "});"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        }

      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "📍 Donations",
      "description": "Kelola titik bantuan: lihat, buat, edit, update status.",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "Lihat Semua Titik (default: Open)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations"] },
            "description": "Ambil semua titik bantuan berstatus **Open** (default).\n\nResponse mengandung `pagination` dan `data`."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "pm.test(\"Ada pagination\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property('pagination');",
              "});",
              "pm.test(\"Ada data array\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().data).to.be.an('array');",
              "});"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Filter by Urgency – Mendesak",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations?urgency=Mendesak",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations"],
              "query": [{ "key": "urgency", "value": "Mendesak", "description": "Mendesak | Normal | Rendah" }]
            },
            "description": "Filter titik berdasarkan tingkat urgensi.\n\n**Nilai valid:** `Mendesak`, `Normal`, `Rendah`"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "pm.test(\"Semua data urgency Mendesak\", () => {",
              "    const data = pm.response.json().data;",
              "    data.forEach(item => pm.expect(item.urgency).to.equal('Mendesak'));",
              "});"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Filter by Status – On Progress",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations?status=On Progress",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations"],
              "query": [{ "key": "status", "value": "On Progress", "description": "Open | On Progress | Completed" }]
            },
            "description": "Tampilkan titik bantuan yang sedang dalam proses.\n\n**Nilai valid:** `Open`, `On Progress`, `Completed`"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Cari by Keyword (?search=)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations?search=banjir",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations"],
              "query": [{ "key": "search", "value": "banjir", "description": "Cari di title dan description (case-insensitive)" }]
            },
            "description": "Full-text search pada `title` dan `description` menggunakan ILIKE.\n\nContoh: `?search=banjir` akan menemukan 'Korban Banjir Kali Code'."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Pagination (?page=&limit=)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations?page=1&limit=2",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page",  "value": "2",  "description": "Halaman ke-n (default: 1)" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "2", "description": "Jumlah per halaman (default: 10, maks: 100)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Uji pagination: ambil 2 data per halaman.\n\nResponse `pagination` berisi `total`, `total_pages`, `current_page`, `limit`."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "pm.test(\"Data maks 2 item\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().data.length).to.be.at.most(2);",
              "});",
              "pm.test(\"Pagination ada total_pages\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().pagination).to.have.property('total_pages');",
              "});"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Gabung Filter + Search + Pagination",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations?urgency=Normal&page=1&limit=5&search=yogya",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "urgency", "value": "Normal" },
                { "key": "page",    "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit",   "value": "5" },
                { "key": "search",  "value": "yogya" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Kombinasikan semua filter sekaligus."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Filter Urgency Tidak Valid",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations?urgency=SangatMendesak",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations"],
              "query": [{ "key": "urgency", "value": "SangatMendesak" }]
            },
            "description": "Uji nilai urgency yang tidak valid.\n\n**Expected:** 400"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 400\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Detail Titik by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations/{{point_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations","{{point_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Ambil detail satu titik bantuan beserta:\n- Koordinat (longitude, latitude)\n- Nama pembuat\n- Rata-rata rating & jumlah rating\n- Jumlah dokumentasi foto\n\n**Expected:** 200\n**Expected jika tidak ada:** 404"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200 atau 404\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect([200, 404]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
              "});",
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    pm.test(\"Ada avg_rating\", () => {",
              "        pm.expect(pm.response.json().data).to.have.property('avg_rating');",
              "    });",
              "}"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Detail Titik – ID Tidak Ada",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations/99999",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations","99999"]
            },
            "description": "Uji akses titik yang tidak ada.\n\n**Expected:** 404"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 404\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(404));"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Titik Terdekat (Nearby) 🔑",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations/nearby?lat={{user_lat}}&lng={{user_lng}}&radius=5000",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations","nearby"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "lat",    "value": "{{user_lat}}", "description": "Latitude posisi user" },
                { "key": "lng",    "value": "{{user_lng}}", "description": "Longitude posisi user" },
                { "key": "radius", "value": "5000",          "description": "Radius dalam meter" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Cari titik bantuan dalam radius tertentu dari posisi user (koordinat default: Yogyakarta).\n\nHasilnya diurutkan dari yang terdekat. Butuh **JWT token**."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "pm.test(\"Ada distance_meters\", () => {",
              "    const data = pm.response.json().data;",
              "    if (data.length > 0) pm.expect(data[0]).to.have.property('distance_meters');",
              "});"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Buat Titik Bantuan ⚡ (auto-save point_id) 🔑",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Bantuan Sembako Pasca Banjir\",\n  \"description\": \"Warga RT 05/RW 02 membutuhkan sembako dan pakaian layak pakai.\",\n  \"longitude\": 110.3695,\n  \"latitude\": -7.7956,\n  \"urgency\": \"Mendesak\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations"] },
            "description": "Buat titik bantuan baru. **Hanya role komunitas.**\n\n`point_id` dari response akan **otomatis tersimpan** ke environment untuk digunakan di request berikutnya.\n\n**Field wajib:** `title`, `longitude`, `latitude`\n**Field opsional:** `description`, `urgency` (default: Normal)"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 201\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
              "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
              "    const id = pm.response.json().data.id;",
              "    pm.environment.set('point_id', id);",
              "    console.log('✅ point_id tersimpan:', id);",
              "}"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Buat Titik – Koordinat Tidak Diisi",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Bantuan tanpa koordinat\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations"] },
            "description": "Uji validasi: koordinat wajib diisi.\n\n**Expected:** 400"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 400\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Edit Titik Bantuan 🔑",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Bantuan Sembako Pasca Banjir (Updated)\",\n  \"urgency\": \"Normal\",\n  \"description\": \"Situasi sudah membaik, bantuan tetap diperlukan.\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations/{{point_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations","{{point_id}}"] },
            "description": "Edit `title`, `description`, dan/atau `urgency` titik bantuan.\n\n**Hanya pengelola (komunitas yang membuat) yang bisa edit.**\n- Minimal satu field harus diisi\n- Tidak bisa edit `location` dan `status` (gunakan endpoint status)\n\n**Expected:** 200\n**Expected jika bukan pengelola:** 403"
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200 atau 403\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect([200, 403]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
              "});"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Update Status → On Progress 🔑",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"On Progress\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/donations/{{point_id}}/status", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","donations","{{point_id}}","status"] },
            "description": "Donatur atau komunitas menandai titik sebagai **On Progress** (sedang ditangani).\n\nTidak memerlukan koordinat user.\n\n**Expected:** 200\n**Catatan:** Hanya titik berstatus `Open` yang bisa diubah ke `On Progress`."
          },
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status harus 200 atau 400\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect([200, 400]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
              "});"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }]
        },

        {
          "name": "Update Status → Completed (Geo-fencing) 🔑",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
